overview: When the checkered flag has been waved, every driver knows that the best way to channel their raging, post-race adrenaline is by heading back to their garage and commanding their crew to 'Fuck Me Fast and Furious.' From visionary directors Raph North and Iza Elle, these nine men live life a lap at a time and know that the only thing more important than burning rubber on the road is busting a thick nut with their team.
title: Fuck Me Fast and Furious
